### SwaRupa API — Phase 1 Endpoint Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080


# ==============================================================
# HEALTH
# ==============================================================

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/health


# ==============================================================
# USERS
# ==============================================================

### 1. Create User
POST http://localhost:8080/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "user_001",
  "display_name": "patrick"
}

---

### 2. Create User — missing id (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "display_name": "No ID User"
}

---

### 3. Get User by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/users/user_001

---

### 4. Get User — not found (expect 404)
GET http://localhost:8080/users/nonexistent_user


# ==============================================================
# ARTISTS
# ==============================================================

### 5. Create Artist — full fields
POST http://localhost:8080/artists
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sunil Edirisinghe",
  "musicbrainz_id": "a74b1b7f-71a5-4011-9441-d0b5e4146738",
  "image_url": "https://example.com/SunilEdirisinghe.jpg",
  "submitted_by": "user_001"
}

---

### 6. Create Artist — minimal (name only)
POST http://localhost:8080/artists
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Thom Yorke"
}

---

### 7. Create Artist — missing name (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/artists
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "image_url": "https://example.com/image.jpg"
}

---

### 8. Get Artist by ID
# Replace ARTIST_ID with the id returned from step 5
GET http://localhost:8080/artists/a471576f-5077-4af2-bb16-a85e13c0ee7d

---

### 9. Get Artist — not found (expect 404)
GET http://localhost:8080/artists/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000


# ==============================================================
# ALBUMS
# ==============================================================
### 10. Create Album — single artist
POST http://localhost:8080/albums
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Sunils album",
  "release_year": 1997,
  "artist_ids": ["a471576f-5077-4af2-bb16-a85e13c0ee7d"],
  "submitted_by": "user_001"
}

---

### 11. Create Album — multiple artists (collaboration)
POST http://localhost:8080/albums
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Collaborative Album",
  "release_year": 2024,
  "artist_ids": ["a471576f-5077-4af2-bb16-a85e13c0ee7d", "ea78e9c8-e3f0-47c4-b027-7aff8d8c2cb9"],
  "submitted_by": "user_001"
}

---

### 12. Create Album — no release year (optional field)
POST http://localhost:8080/albums
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Untitled Album",
  "artist_ids": ["a471576f-5077-4af2-bb16-a85e13c0ee7d"]
}

---

### 13. Create Album — missing title (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/albums
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "release_year": 2024,
  "artist_ids": ["a471576f-5077-4af2-bb16-a85e13c0ee7d"]
}

---

### 14. Create Album — missing artist_ids (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/albums
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "No Artists Album"
}

---

### 15. Create Album — empty artist_ids (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/albums
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Empty Artists",
  "artist_ids": []
}

---

### 16. Create Album — invalid artist_id that doesn't exist in DB (expect 500, FK violation)
POST http://localhost:8080/albums
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Bad Artist Ref",
  "artist_ids": ["00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"]
}

---

### 17. Get Album by ID — should include artists array
# Replace ALBUM_ID with the id returned from step 10
GET http://localhost:8080/albums/f5527ad3-6e7c-4f98-81da-0fc396b6c5d2

---

### 18. Get Album — collaboration (should show both artists)
# Replace COLLAB_ALBUM_ID with the id returned from step 11
GET http://localhost:8080/albums/338563cd-3d8d-4f8d-bcff-18f540ae4411

---

### 19. Get Album — not found (expect 404)
GET http://localhost:8080/albums/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000


# ==============================================================
# ARTWORKS
# ==============================================================

### 20. Submit Artwork — full fields
POST http://localhost:8080/albums/f5527ad3-6e7c-4f98-81da-0fc396b6c5d2/artworks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "source_id": "coverartarchive_001",
  "image_url": "https://example.com/ok-computer-cover.jpg",
  "thumbnail_url": "https://example.com/ok-computer-thumb.jpg",
  "is_official": true,
  "submitted_by": "user_001"
}

---

### 21. Submit Artwork — minimal (image_url only)
POST http://localhost:8080/albums/f5527ad3-6e7c-4f98-81da-0fc396b6c5d2/artworks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "image_url": "https://example.com/fan-art.jpg"
}

---

### 22. Submit Artwork — unofficial fan art
POST http://localhost:8080/albums/f5527ad3-6e7c-4f98-81da-0fc396b6c5d2/artworks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "image_url": "https://example.com/fanart2.jpg",
  "is_official": false,
  "submitted_by": "user_001"
}

---

### 23. Submit Artwork — missing image_url (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/albums/f5527ad3-6e7c-4f98-81da-0fc396b6c5d2/artworks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "thumbnail_url": "https://example.com/thumb.jpg"
}

---

### 24. Get all artworks for album — no filters
GET http://localhost:8080/albums/f5527ad3-6e7c-4f98-81da-0fc396b6c5d2/artworks

---

### 25. Get artworks — filter by pending status
GET http://localhost:8080/albums/f5527ad3-6e7c-4f98-81da-0fc396b6c5d2/artworks?status=pending

---

### 26. Get artworks — filter by approved status
GET http://localhost:8080/albums/f5527ad3-6e7c-4f98-81da-0fc396b6c5d2/artworks?status=approved

---

### 27. Get artworks — filter by rejected status
GET http://localhost:8080/albums/f5527ad3-6e7c-4f98-81da-0fc396b6c5d2/artworks?status=rejected

---

### 28. Get artworks — official only
GET http://localhost:8080/albums/f5527ad3-6e7c-4f98-81da-0fc396b6c5d2/artworks?official=true

---

### 29. Get artworks — sorted by priority score
GET http://localhost:8080/albums/f5527ad3-6e7c-4f98-81da-0fc396b6c5d2/artworks?sort=priority

---

### 30. Get artworks — combined filter: official + priority sort
GET http://localhost:8080/albums/f5527ad3-6e7c-4f98-81da-0fc396b6c5d2/artworks?official=true&sort=priority

---

### 31. Get artworks — combined filter: approved + priority sort
GET http://localhost:8080/albums/f5527ad3-6e7c-4f98-81da-0fc396b6c5d2/artworks?status=approved&sort=priority

---

### 32. Get artworks — album with no artworks (expect empty array [])
# Use an album ID that has no artworks submitted yet
GET http://localhost:8080/albums/ALBUM_ID_EMPTY/artworks
